</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P4953  Refuse Systems.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>RES  Capital expenditures.
    RES  Facilities.
