<HEADLINE>
FT  13 JAN 93 / AEEU to vote on TUC affiliation
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE executive committee of the AEEU engineering and electricians union
agreed yesterday to hold a postal ballot of members over affiliating to the
Trades Union Congress (TUC). The executive will urge members to vote in
favour of the move, which comes 4 1/2 years after the EETPU electricians'
union was expelled from the TUC.
The EETPU merged with the AEU engineering workers' union last year to form
the AEEU.
