<TEXT>
DE BEERS led a recovery in prices in afternoon trading with a 75-cent rise
to R66. However, the overall index finished 3 down at 3,408, industrials
slipped 6 to 4,556 and the gold index lost 12 to 789. Anglos fell 75 cents
to R96.50.
